title: Democrats to meet after primary
content: The Chino Valley Democrats will meet at 7 p.m. Monday, June 11 at Archibald’s Drive-Thru, 15421 Fairfield Ranch Road in Chino Hills to discuss the results of the June 5 primary and strategies for the November general election. The public is invited. Membership is open to all registered Democrats who support the principles of the Democratic Party.    Information: Marian Arguello, 591-1864 or chinovalleydems@gmail.com .
